Update on one of my favourite #womenownedbusiness , @wearpepper - (bra company specializing in small boobs) - much to my delight, they launched swimwear!👙 The fit is great, I flapped around in the sea and not one boob escaped. There are a variety of colors and styles.
.
Pepper swim is ethically made in Columbia by a factory which pays fair market wage and employs 85% women, mostly single mothers. 35% of water used during the dyeing process is recycled.
.
Next time you or a small boobed person your life needs swimwear, consider using my code if you wanna get something.
"MIASAVAGE" for 20% off
.
#woc #aapiwomenlead #swimwear #womenownedsmallbusiness #ethicalfashion #wocowned #wearpepper #smallboobs

I've had the pleasure of working with many makeup artists and I'm consistently amazed how they are able to work with such an inconsistent, moving canvas as the human face. None of my paintings sweat lol.
One of the very best in the SoCal area is @elizabethrootmakeup , who did this on me ^ | If you need someone for editorial or event work, especially for a natural approach, check out her gorgeous portfolio. 
.
Not an ad I just love her work
